  "summary": "“I see life through vibrations. A summer’s night of dance, shining brighter with each camera flare. To feel the world is to believe in balance. There is no perfect memory. Only beautiful thoughts. ‘Confetti’ is an experimental collection that revolves around an embrace of the disco aesthetic and dancehall immersion.” — Nygilia",
